0xf675a87397a6239eaf95ad948670a5b19d076c.description: Love is in the Air is a masterpiece that epitomizes the unparalleled creative insurgency of Banksyâ€™s oeuvre. Characterised by its recognisable subject, graphic force and visual directness, this iconic work has helped cement Banksyâ€™s place as an a decisive political gadfly for our time. Particle acquired the piece at auction on 5/13/2021 and the work was subsequently donated to the non-profit Particle Foundation where the piece will remain in perpetuity. Love is in the Air is the first piece offered by Particle representing a peaceful revolution, changing the narrative of ownership, and enabling anyone to collect, experience, and enjoy the masterpiece.
